Who: LORD ELDER, Elita
Location: Ark - Command Center

> "Then he opened comlink to lord Elder "Lord Elder, he
> situation here has complicated... a bit"he knew that Elita may be listening
> so he didnt liked to worry her"I'm trying to escape the Blackfortress with
> Nightlight, Rodimus and tucson are trying to rescue windlord" he typed an
> encoded message to Him "Nightlight isnt in condition to see her daughter, we
> will need a place to hold her while she is reprogramed and we need to keep
> elita away from her"
>
> Then the old autobot took Nighlight and continue his trip towards the exit

Lord Elder nodded as he got the message and then the second encoded
message as well. "I understand." Elder said as he glanced over at
Elita and then back at the messages coming in.

"We are ready to provide what ever assistance we can." Elder said to
Kup as well as the others Autobots and Maximals. "Whatever help that
can be spared from the old Maximal base is on the way as well. I
believe I heard Legacy say he was going, and I would imagine Talon."

Elder shrugged, "I haven't heard anything from Perseus and the rest of
his crew over there."

(TAG)

Preston
